  "guide.bakeries.categories.bread_making_process": "§6饢之所製",
  "guide.bakeries.categories.food_ingredient": "§6材",
  "guide.bakeries.entries.yeast_making": "酵母所製",
  "guide.bakeries.entries.yeast_making.descr": "欲製囊也，先以其糰，則需$(gold)酵母/$。先備一酵罐入$(gold)三$(l:food_ingredient/flour)全麥末/$$(gold)並一瓶水/$，而待其畢也，則可以琉璃瓶出鮮酵母也。",
  "guide.bakeries.entries.baked_bread": "饢之所焙",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.baked_bread":"得焙爐也？得則可以焙饢也！麵胚之物者，下示其所溫也。調其溫而入胚，則可待其出也。",
  "guide.bakeries.entries.prepare_the_dough":"麵糰之備",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.prepare_the_dough": "有$(l:yeast_making)酵母/$則可始作麵糰也。當需一$(l:baking_utensil/blander)混拌械/$以製。",
  "guide.bakeries.entries.create_bread_dough": "麵胚之製",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.create_bread_dough": "既揉之麵糰者，復入$(gold)胚案/$，則可覽其可所製之饢胚也，左擊以擇而製。",
  "guide.bakeries.entries.milk": "乳",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.milk": "乳瓶入手，$(gold)右擊晃之/$，俄而其質變也。",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.milk_2": "一晃",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.milk_3": "二晃",
  "guide.bakeries.entries.flour": "麥末",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.flour": "$(l:baking_utensil/flour_sieve)麥末篩/$篩全麥末為麥末",
  "guide.bakeries.categories.perfect_temperature":"§6全美火候",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.perfect_temperature": "全美火候之焙食者，飢滿亦可食之也。",
  "guide.bakeries.entries.salt": "營火煮鹵",
  "guide.bakeries.entries.salt_2": "粗鹽塊",
  "guide.bakeries.entries.salt_3": "鹽礦",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.salt": "可以營火煮鹽水以得粗鹽。",
  "guide.bakeries.categories.baking_utensil": "§6焙之器具",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.flour_sieve": "麥末篩者，篩物者也，夫若$(l:food_ingredient/flour)麥末/$者也。",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.mould": "製若殊形之食者，蓋將用之。",
  "guide.bakeries.categories.do_you_know": "焉得知之？",
  "guide.bakeries.entries.await": "待",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.await": "現實焉，製饢須以久之酵澥也。",
  "guide.bakeries.entries.be_unable_to_eat_any_more": "食不完，何以食完？",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.be_unable_to_eat_any_more": "是嘗可淬靈修繕，亦可以耐久邪？",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.bread_knife": "可以切饢，夫若艸市饢。",
  "guide.bakeries.entries.cheese.descr": "先備一酵罐，入一桶乳、一$(l:food_ingredient/salt)鹽/$而待其畢也，則可出乳酪塊焉。",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.cocoa_powder": "$(l:baking_utensil/flour_sieve)麥末篩/$篩可可荳為其末。",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.blender": "混拌械者，君之焙途之重器也，可以混拌蕃物，夫若麵糰麵糊。",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.blender_2": "可以赤石炬更其式，則可置設所濾。",
  "guide.bakeries.entries.feed_sequence": "入料有序",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.feed_sequence": "麵糰之製也，入料之有序也，先乾末、則酵母、則液、則黃油。",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.meat_floss": "$(l:baking_utensil/blander)混拌械/$作豕炙為肉鬆。",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.whole_egg": "可利手持卵、非利手持饢刀以得之，右擊全卵以分之。",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.tomato": "可賈與農夫而得。",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.olive": "可賈與農夫而得。",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.raw_coffee_bean": "嗅獸可掘之於叢莽。",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.moka_pot": "可以模咖壺烹玄茶。",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.moka_pot_2": "置壺上，右擊入玄茶末，俄而烹畢。",
  "guide.bakeries.entries.moka_pot": "模咖壺烹玄茶",
  "guide.bakeries.categories.cake_making_process": "§6洋糕所製",
  "guide.bakeries.entries.prepare_the_paste": "備麵糊",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.prepare_the_paste": "需以$(l:baking_utensil/blander)混拌械/$製糊，先製發卵白、卵黃糊，而混之。",
  "guide.bakeries.entries.star_baking": "入模以焙",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.star_baking": "洋糕糊入模也。焙之必需一模，雖可異也。罷則入焙爐焉。",
  "guide.bakeries.entries.sequence_assembly": "列組",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.sequence_assembly": "蕃材入胚以製高等之洋糕也！",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.sequence_assembly_2": "洋糕胚片→乳油→洋糕胚片→乳油→甜莓",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.sequence_assembly_3": "玄茶潤洋糕胚片→乳酪乳油→玄茶潤洋糕胚片→乳酪乳油→可可末",
  "guide.bakeries.descr.sequence_assembly_4": "赤絲絨洋糕胚→乳酪乳油",
  "guide.bakeries.categories.descr.bread_making_process": "饢製小學",
  "guide.bakeries.categories.descr.cake_making_process": "洋糕所製小學",
  "guide.bakeries.entries.fresh_cheese_cube": "鮮乳酪塊",
